**Meomiry Station** is a pastel-themed online photobooth where users can create cute photo strips with filters, stickers, and aesthetic templates. Users can take photos directly from their camera or upload existing photos, apply fun visual styles, and export their own photobooth strips.

Inspired by Korean photobooth culture and Gen-Z aesthetic design.

